section#ticket_buy(aria-label="ticket_buy")
    h2 Get your ticket
        a.header-anchor(href="#ticket_buy" aria-hidden="true")= anchorSymbol

    h3 Option 1 - Buy it at the door
    p.l--columns--2.
        All tickets can be bought at the door, so far we always had enough space for everybody who showed up.
        Due to paypal fees, day-tickets can be only bought at the door.

    h3 Option 2 - Get it now! <i>(recommended)</i>
    p.l--columns--2.
        The pre-sale has started! Buying your ticket beforehand will help us being more fluid beforehand (since the festival is non-profit) and better plan ahead how many people will show up, how many T-Shirts have to be bought and so on.
        If you buy a ticket, but can't come, we will of course will refund you.

    h4 Pay via Paypal Checkout

    div.paypal
        p.paypal__description.
            Please use the form to get your ticket. You will get an email-confirmation including your ticket code and we will put you on the guestlist.


